Package application

Class Student

java.lang.Object
application.User
application.Student
All Implemented Interfaces:
StudentCampOptions
Direct Known Subclasses:
StudentCommittee
public class Student extends User implements StudentCampOptions
Account type for User. Its exclusive complement is Staff. Students exclusively have the rights to join Camps and write enquiries. Students can also sign up to be StudentCommittee, so no Student object should be inititalised as Student. It should be initialied as StudentCommittee and immediately cast up to Student.

    • signUpView

      public void signUpView(List<User> userList, List<Camp> campList, List<Signup> signupList)
      General menu for Camps the Student can sign up for.
      The conditions checked for an eligible Camp are as follows:
      Same faculty or "ALL"
      Not already signed up or Committee
      Not blacklisted
      Camp registration date not past
      Camp still have empty spots.
      Parameters:
      userList - List of all User objects. Used to save user state.
      campList - List of all Camp objects. Used for camp data.
      signupList - List of all Signup objects. Used to save signup state.
